value.0: The member of the Amnian army was characteristically cruel, opportunistic, and mercenary.
This well made halberd was crafted during the Interregnum and still functions exceptionally, even though the civil war ended a few years ago.
The halberd is the most common polearm, and could be called a cross between a spear and an axe.  Such weapons are often mass-produced for militia, and serve well when defending against marauders.
